longBusinessSummary: Mariner Corporation Limited operates as a diversified investment company in Australia and China. It invests in properties, loan books, agricultural assets, aged care, office buildings, plant and equipment, subdivision developments, and others, as well as operates as a lessor of plant and equipment. The company was incorporated in 1985 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
